        "action": "Require all UK betting shops to have security screens to protect staff.",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The Gambling Commission recommends such screens but it is down to the Local Authority who issue licences whether or not they are needed. It should be a legal requirement for all Betting Shops to have safety screens. All Betting Shops should have them, like banks and Post Offices do.",
